meta {
  name: 01 - Get artist (cold)
  type: http
  seq: 1
}

get {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/catalog/artists/{{beatlesArtistMbid}}
}

headers {
  Cookie: better-auth.session_token={{sessionCookie}}
}

docs {
  First call on an unseeded MBID → expect 202 with { jobId, pollUrl }.
  Hit this 5 times in a row — all responses return the same jobId (dedup via
  BullMQ deterministic job IDs).
}
